com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.constraint
Interface ConstraintRoot

public interface ConstraintRoot

A representation of the model object 'Root'.

The following features are supported:

  • Mixed
  • XMLNS Prefix Map
  • XSI Schema Location
  • Constraint And
  • Constraint Collocation
  • Constraint Communication
  • Constraint Deferred Hosting
  • Constraint Enumeration
  • Constraint Exclusion
  • Constraint Group Cardinality
  • Constraint Member Cardinality
  • Constraint Not
  • Constraint Or
  • Constraint Range
  • Constraint Type
  • Constraint Version
  • Constraint Xor
  • Value

See Also:
ConstraintPackage.getConstraintRoot()
